snippet.title: The Adderall Diaries: James Franco & Pamela Romanowsky Exclusive Interview | ScreenSlam
snippet.description:
RELEASE DATE: April 15, 2016

DIRECTOR: Pamela Romanowsky

CAST: James Franco, Ed Harris, Amber Heard, Christian Slater, Wilmer Valderrama, Cynthia Nixon, Jim Parrack

PLOT: Author Steven Elliot has a fascination with a high-profile murder case in which leads him to his own troubled past. The case brings him to a new romance with Lana Edmond, and confront his issues with his abusive father Neil.
